around the point  at time .

Actually, the extra term that appeared in () due to the
noncommutativity is not responsible for any inconsistency of the theory, but
its role must be understood. One way to justify its presence is to perceive
that it is essential in order to assure that the equivariance 
property is satisfied by . This
means that if  at
some time , then  for
all . In other words,  preserves its form as a functional of
